Apache/FilteringProxy version 0.1
=================================

The Apache::FilteringProxy module provides a rewriting proxy for HTTP servers.
This module was originally created to allow remote access of resources that are
restricted to using IP-based authentication.

INSTALLATION

    To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

    This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    LWP::UserAgent
    XML::EasyOBJ

